Ing '''Ugnayang pangmalda'''  '''Public relations''' o ('''PR''') ing dapat a pamanibala king pamikalat ning [[impormasyun]] pilatan ning indibidwal o between an individual or [[aguman]] o organisasyun ampo ing [[Pangkabilugang malda|malda]] o publiku (''public'').<ref>Grunig, James E. and Hunt, Todd. Managing Public Relations. (Orlando, FL: Harcourt Brace Jovanovich, 1984), 6e.</ref> Malyaring iyabe king ugnayang pangmalda ing aguman o [[individual]] a miraras king malda kapamilatan ning pamangamit kareng paksang pangpublikung interes ampong balitang e mangaylangang diretsung pamamayad.<ref>Seitel, Fraser P. The Practice of Public Relations. (Upper Saddle River, NJ: Pearson Prentice Hall, 2007), 10e.</ref> Ing parasan o kapagnasan ning ugnayang pangmalda ya pin ing pamagkumbinsi king malda o publiku, deng mamuhunan (''investors''), kasosyu (''partners''), empleadyu, ampong reng aliwang sektor a maki interes keting mika partikular a pamalak o paglalawe tungkul kaniti, deng kayang manibala, produktu, o desisyung pampulitika. Kayabe la kareng aktibidad a makaugne keti deng pamagsalita kareng kumperensya, pamanyambut galal king industria, pamakiugnayan kareng pahayagan, ampong komunikasyun kareng empleyadu.<ref>Rubel, Gina F., Everyday Public Relations for Lawyers, Doylestown, PA: 1 ed. 2007, ISBN 978-0-9801719-0-7</ref>

